      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "The 311-nts ssRNA template, formed by the fusion of a heterologous sequence (171-nts) to the 5'-end of a 140-nts fragment corresponding to the 3'-end region of the TaV 3'-UTR  , was produced by in vitro transcription, using as template the pRSET-A/TaV-3'UTR plasmid described below."
